{
  "_README": "Template config. Copy to appsettings.json (gitignored) and fill secrets, OR provide secrets via environment variables (double underscore), e.g. Security__ApiKey, ConnectionStrings__SupabaseDb, ObjectStorage__AccessKey, ObjectStorage__SecretKey. Env vars override appsettings.json. Non-secret values below are the intended defaults.",
